:name:
Dominator

:coretxt:
Control over over single person. Any opposed check is done with \AbilityNameCharm{} and are resisted with \AbilityNameResist{}.

:cost:
1 Reason

:req:
You have seduced someone who before that hated you.

:1:
Issue single clear command and target will obey.

:2:
Rewrite memory of target.
Can also be used to rewrite personality, though this is slower.

:3:
Posses someone.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMindControl
